<LegalLayout
  title="Terms of Use"
  description="The terms that govern your use of devngn.ai, the human-first developer wellness service."
  kicker="Legal"
  updated="June 9, 2026"
>
  <p>
    Welcome to <strong>devngn.ai</strong>. These Terms of Use ("Terms") govern your
    access to and use of the devngn.ai website, APIs, client packages, and the
    wellness service (together, the "Service"). By using the Service you agree to
    these Terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the Service.
  </p>

  <h2>1. What devngn.ai is</h2>
  <p>
    devngn.ai is human-first developer wellness. With your explicit opt-in, it
    notices real gaps in your schedule and nudges you with short, five-second
    movement breaks tuned to your profile, your goals, and the equipment you
    actually have. It is designed to help the human at the keyboard move, breathe,
    and reset.
  </p>

  <h2>2. Health disclaimer</h2>
  <p>
    The Service offers general wellness and movement suggestions. It is
    <strong>not medical advice</strong> and is not a substitute for professional
    care. Movement prompts are general-purpose and may not be appropriate for
    everyone. Always listen to your body, stop anything that causes pain, and
    consult a qualified health professional before starting any new physical
    activity, especially if you have an injury or medical condition. You
    participate in any suggested activity at your own risk.
  </p>

  <h2>3. Opt-in and your account</h2>
