    You can read the full license on
    <a href="https://github.com/IEvangelist/devngn.ai/blob/main/LICENSE" rel="noopener" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>5. Acceptable use</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Don't misuse, disrupt, or attempt to break the Service or its infrastructure.</li>
    <li>Don't access data that isn't yours or that hasn't been shared with you.</li>
